infoparam.value:
Fibonnaci: Amount of do!1 configures the fibonacci number. The first one is for initial conditions only.
Example:
3 do!1 computes fibonnaci(2) which is 2
# do!1 | n1 | n2 | result ---------------------- 1 | 0 | 1 | 1 2 | 0 | 1 | 1 3 | 1 | 1 | 2 4 | 2 | 2 | 4 5 | 4 | 4 | 8 . . . . . . . .
